<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl/><http_method>GET</http_method><name>validategdsp</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
    var jsonArr = [];
	var gdsp_id = request.queryParams.gdsp_id.toString();
	var ned_id = request.queryParams.ned_id.toString();
	var association = '';
    var base_id = gdsp_id.substring(8);
	var real_gdsp_id = 'NCI-RITM' + base_id;
	
	var cat_items = new GlideRecord('sc_cat_item');
	cat_items.addQuery('short_description','CCR Genomic Data Sharing Plan');
	cat_items.query();
	cat_items.next();
	var cat_item_number = cat_items.getValue('sys_id');
	
	var req_items = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
	
//	req_items.addQuery('opened_by.employee_number', ned_id);
	req_items.addQuery('number', real_gdsp_id);
	req_items.addQuery('cat_item',cat_item_number);
	req_items.query();
	if(req_items.getRowCount() > 0){
		association = "True";
	}else{
		association = "False";
	}
	var obj_id = '';
	if(association == 'False'){
		if (base_id.indexOf('-') == -1) {
			association = "False";
		}else {
			var real_id = base_id.substring(0, base_id.indexOf('-'));
			var tracking_items = new GlideRecord('u_ccr_tracking_t');
			tracking_items.addQuery('u_ticket_number', 'CONTAINS', real_id);
			tracking_items.query();
		
			if (tracking_items.getRowCount() >0 ) {
				tracking_items.next();
		
				obj_id = tracking_items.u_orgid;
				var req_items1 = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
				req_items1.addQuery('contact_type','CONTAINS', obj_id);
				req_items1.query();
				if(req_items1.getRowCount() > 0){
					association = "True";
				}else{
					association = "False";
				}
			}else {
				association = "False";
			}
		}
	}

	jsonArr.push({
		ned_id: ned_id.toString(),
		gdsp_id: gdsp_id.toString(),
		association: association.toString(),
	});
   return jsonArr;

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/naci/ccr_gds_rest/validategdsp</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/validategdsp</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>false</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>false</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-03-08 17:16:49</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>2c23c00fdbd9b20054d8ff621f961911</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>validategdsp</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_2c23c00fdbd9b20054d8ff621f961911</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>wuye@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-07-19 19:36:29</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ccr_gds_rest">3d03404fdbd9b20054d8ff621f9619d6</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>
